item.title: Bulgarian Split Squat
item.description: The individual places one foot on the ground and the toes of the other foot on a raised surface behind them, with the legs straight.

item.title: Beat Your Boot
item.description: The feet are placed together on the ground and the individual bends at the waist to grab the ankles, with the legs kept straight.

item.title: Ham Sandwich
item.description: The individual kneels on the ground, with the feet anchored under a solid surface, or held to the ground by another person.

item.title: Bam Bams
item.description: The individual lies in a prone position on a raised, horizontal surface so the legs may project freely beyond the edge of the surface and the toes rest on the ground.

item.title: King Of The Klutz
item.description: The individual stands on one leg, body held vertically, closes the eyes, then holds the position for as long as possible.

item.title: Hip Extension
item.description: The individual starts with the back resting on the ground, and the legs bent at 90 degrees with the feet resting on an elevated surface such as a chair.

item.title: One-Legged Romanian Dead Lift
item.description: The individual starts in a standing position with the feet together.

item.title: Standing Leg Curl
item.description: The individual starts with the feet shoulder-width apart.

item.title: Standing Side Leg Lift
item.description: The individual stands with their feet hip-width apart.

item.title: Dirty Dogs
item.description: The individual starts in an all-fours position, then lifts one knee off the ground and swings the knee out to the side as far as possible, maintaining the bent knee at a 90-degree angle.
